data.description: Nothing to do but move in!  Don't miss this beautiful 2 story home in Carol Stream school district that is walking distance to Elsie C. Johnson Elementary School.  This home has 2 huge beautiful first floor additions.  The family room off the kitchen with attached dinning room and sliding door that opens up to the backyard.  There is a HUGE first floor bedroom with 2 closets and sliding door to back yard, use as a bedroom or as a private work from home office the possibilities are endless.  3 bedrooms upstairs with master suite.  The whole house has been freshly painted and new carpet installed September 2020.  The amazing backyard has a 2 story shed with electricity that is any handyman's dream!  This house is just waiting for you to make it your own!
